name: Recycled Leather Obi Belt- Black
description:
Made from recycled or leather remnants.
One-Size fits all.  
This is a black obi belt with black ties.  It is versatile and can be worn a number of ways.  It is made with post-manufacturer recycled materials.  The leather is extremely soft and malleable.  The ties are made of a cotton/ lycra knit fabric.

FREE SHIPPING
